      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AUBURN QUEEN (1) goes very well this course and distance starting six times for two wins and three minors. Was out of the placings last time (23.41) at Q Lakeside in a Free For All, finishing eighth and beaten 52 lengths. Looks suited and should go close. ZABDON NO DOUBT (7) was among the minors three back at this track then missed the frame the last two, but drawn box 7 this time where she has won before. Can improve sharply here. SWEET LADETTE (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 25.31 beating Holly's Bear. Likely to be in the finish. CALM AND CRUISY (8) is likely to have admirers.",
